{"tid":995173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？日出康城地盤電工被拖薪百萬","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T10:32:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62b5bf46ddc265a1708bb124793ae64199f00cbf","tid":995173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"年近歲晚，約30名將軍澳日出康城第六期一至二座地盤電工被拖欠薪金，工人今早(25日)到地盤示威。協助工友的建築地盤職工總會組織幹事何天忻指，僱主本月初解僱這批四判工人，拖欠12月及1月的工資、加班費、代通知金及假期薪金等，合共100萬港元。工人曾多次直接向僱主、大判及二判追討，但無音信，因此發起今次示威行動。<br />\n<br />\n何表示，工人透露有人未付工程費，以致拖欠薪金，工人剛與大判及二判談判，得悉三判下午將會帶同工友資料到地盤核對，承諾發放欠薪。她指，如果出糧承諾未有兌現，工人不排除行動升級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125113116173-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fbkn-20190125113116173-0125_00822_001.html&d=9I4BeS4eQ9jGYJ6jP2Db67IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6edb634d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125113116173-0125_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"16021b9232bb9625ea683d3fe9fe4c6b6d7b828c","tid":995173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125113116173-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190125122359\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125113116173-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190125122359&h=0cfb87d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d03af7528396ea5800d1f5dc1b28703cb6dac4a3","tid":995173,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"工人曾多次直接向僱主、大判及二判追討，但無音信<br />\n工人曾多次直接向僱主、大判及二判追討，但無音信<br />\n工人曾多次直接向僱主、大判及二判追討，但無音信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc02b66ebde0615868c142c5e2d78efb9125e9bd","tid":995173,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco